title: Airfoil - 4.8.3 [Intel/KG]
description:
Whats new in Airfoil 4.8.3?

An issue where remote speakers failed to unmute has been corrected.
The Instant On component has been updated to version 7.1.2, fixing several small issues.
Several other small bugs and crashes have been fixed.


Airfoil allows you to send any audio to AirPort Express units, Apple TVs, 
and even other Macs and PCs, all in sync! Its your audio - everywhere.


Installation Note

1. Open the .DMG file you have downloaded
2. Open Airfoil (main program)
3. Once you are in Airfoil, go to your menu bar at the top > Click 'Airfoil' > Click 'Licensing'
4. Open the CORE KG in the .DMG you've opened during step 1 and follow the instructions for copying to clipboard etcetera.
5. Go back to Airfoil's licensing window and fill in the corresponding name and license key from the CORE KG.

Thats it, now you are ready to go!
Enjoy!
